        public boolean addProcessor(NoteStoringPostProcessor processor)
        Description copied from interface: NoteStoringPostProcessorManager
        Add a processor. If there is already a processor with the same type, nothing will happen. If the ID of the processor contains space characters they will be replaced by underscores.
        Specified by:
        addProcessor in interface NoteStoringPostProcessorManager
        Parameters:

        Returns:

             throws TaskAlreadyExistsException
        Description copied from interface: NoteStoringPostProcessorManager

        Specified by:
